== Troubleshooting

*LSDTopoTools* is research software, and unfortunately it can misbehave. In this appendix we list common problems associated with running of the code. 

include::sections/Segmentation.asc[]

=== Summary

If you have a problem that is not listed here, please contact the http://www.geos.ed.ac.uk/homes/smudd[lead developer] of *LSDTopoTools*, and the team will try to find a solution and post it in this appendix. 